casebody.head_matter:
George E. KERSEY, Petitioner,
v.
HERB CHAMBERS 1186, INC., et al.
No. 19-5249
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
